::DeathScythe/Ramulus::

SnowCat's trick worked, DeathScythe was send flying pase her, stopping 
against a rather large tree when he tried to turn. He falls to the ground, 
jumping up a second later. This was obvioustly not working, a different 
strategy was in order. He jumps upwards, his jets activating again.

DeathScythe bursts out of the canopy, flying after SnowCat above the trees. 
Now that there were no trees in his way, he was going much faster, and his 
scanners were locked on to SnowCat's signature. The assassin calmly flies 
above the forest, following SnowCat.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Ramulus frowns as he runs by a large tree, stopping and looking back at it. 
It was splashed with mechfluid and dented: something obvioustly crashed into 
it, something big. The Maximal checks his scanners. The bot he had been 
following was flying again, and there was a second signature running in front 
of it.

Ramulus takes off at a gallop for the second signature, activating his 
comm-link.

"New bot," he says into it, addressing SnowCat, "What's your alliegence?"
